These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, collecting, board-games, magic-tricks
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, water-polo, climbing, cycling
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##8
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks  | woodworking | board-games | collecting  |
| Sport   | soccer | climbing   | cycling  | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, pineapple, lime, onion
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, dancer, fisherman, paramedic
1. the paramedic is not to the left of the paramedic##8
2. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
3. the person eating cucumber is the dancer##1
4. the person eating onion is between the person eating cucumber and the person eating pineapple##2
5. the person eating pineapple is somewhere between the person eating lime and the architect##7
6. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
7. the architect is not to the left of the architect##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | lime | pineapple          | onion | cucumber     |
| Job    | fisherman      | paramedic | architect | dancer |

