.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, accountant, teacher, police-officer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, musical, time-travel, horror
1. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the teacher##8
2. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
3. the accountant is on the right of the software-developer##1
4. the accountant is in an even position##4
5. the police-officer is on the far left or far right##3
6. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
7. the police-officer is the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | software-developer | accountant | teacher     | police-officer |
| Movie-Genre   | musical    | horror   | action | time-travel    |

