.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, reggae, folk, pop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, ice-hockey, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##8
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
4. the fan of pop is not to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
5. the fan of d&b is the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
7. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the fan of pop##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | folk   | reggae         | pop   | d&b    |
| Sport         | sailing | snowboarding | ice-hockey | climbing |

