.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, animation, superhero, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, tennis, badminton
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere between the person watching sports movies and the person watching animation movies##7
2. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching sports movies##7
4. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##8
5. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere between the person watching animation movies and the person who's sport is lacrosse##7
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8
8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | superhero | martial-arts | sports    |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | badminton   | tennis   | lacrosse |

