The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, r&b, soul, rock
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the person eating raspberry##5
3. the person eating apple is on the right of the fan of soul##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
5. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
6. the person eating mango is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
7. the person eating mango is the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | mango | raspberry | banana  | apple |
| Music-Genre   | r&b   | rock         | soul | hip-hop |

