.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, soy-milk, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, weightlifting, golf, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person who's sport is golf##7
3. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is handball##5
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the left of the person who's sport is handball##8
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
7. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea      | soy-milk | lemonade | coffee   |
| Sport      | handball | golf | snowboarding  | weightlifting |

