3. the coach is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere between the person who's sport is biathlon and the coach##7
5. the security-guard is not to the right of the dancer##8
6. the dancer is somewhere between the person who's sport is biathlon and the security-guard##7

.:: Answer ::.
