.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, r&b, blues, country
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, scooter, roller, jet-ski
1. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of country and the person driving the train##2
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
4. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
5. the person driving the scooter is the person driving the scooter##1
6. the fan of blues is not the person driving the roller##6
7. the fan of country is not to the right of the fan of blues##8
8. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | country   | hip-hop | blues | r&b |
| Transport     | jet-ski | scooter       | train  | roller    |

