.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, lettuce, pear, grapes
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, hiking, singing, chess
1. the person eating pear is not to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##8
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person eating lettuce##8
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating pear is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person eating lettuce is on the far left##1
7. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | lettuce        | grapes | pear      | apricot    |
| Hobby   | video-games | singing   | hiking | chess |

