The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, tennis, cycling, rugby
1. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
2. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the person drinking iced-tea##7
7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
8. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | milk | iced-tea         | sprite    | tea       |
| Sport      | tennis | rugby | soccer | cycling |

