.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, garlic, kiwi, lettuce
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, epic, scientific, thriller
 1. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
 2. the person eating lettuce is not to the left of the person eating kiwi##8
 3. the person eating pepper is the person watching scientific movies##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person watching epic movies##8
 5. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating kiwi##5
 7. the person watching epic movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating pepper is not to the right of the person watching scientific movies##8
 9. the person watching epic movies is not to the left of the person eating pepper##8
10. the person eating garlic is not to the left of the person watching documentary movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | garlic    | kiwi | pepper | lettuce |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | thriller  | scientific     | epic    |

