.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, mouse, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, subway, ship, motorbike
1. the owner of the turtle is not the person driving the ship##6
2. the person driving the ship is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
3. the owner of the goat is somewhere between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the turtle##7
4. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
5. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
6. the person driving the train is not to the right of the person driving the subway##8
7. the owner of the goat is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | chinchilla  | turtle | goat  | mouse  |
| Transport   | train | subway   | motorbike | ship |

