.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, guinea-pig, cat, bird
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, airplane, roller, quad-bike
1. the person driving the airplane is not the owner of the dog##6
2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
4. the owner of the cat is the person driving the bus##1
5. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the bus##7
6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
7. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the quad-bike and the owner of the cat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | guinea-pig    | bird | dog | cat |
| Transport   | airplane | quad-bike      | roller     | bus     |

 